**/node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.env
.env.local
.env.*
!.env.example
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.claude/
# Un-ignore tracked Claude Code config: hooks + settings.json live under .claude/
# and must be committed so every agent session inherits the same enforcement.
# Defensive: kept here in case .gitignore is rewritten without this allowance.
!.claude/
!.claude/hooks/
!.claude/hooks/**
!.claude/settings.json

# Agent/session artifacts
# Note: top-level CLAUDE.md is a tracked pointer file to AGENTS.md (the canonical
# contract). Session/scratch CLAUDE notes belong elsewhere (under docs/ or in
# .claude/). Do NOT re-ignore CLAUDE.md without also updating AGENTS.md guidance.
docs/ADMIN_CLAUDE_CODE_SESSIONS.md
docs/CLAUDE_CODE_SESSIONS*.md
docs/SESSION_*.md
docs/DECISION*.md
docs/MEMORY.md
docs/auto-memory/
docs/REPLAN_*.md
docs/REVISION_DIFF.md
docs/PREFLIGHT_REPORT.md
docs/CONSISTENCY_REPORT_*.md
docs/COVERAGE_GAP.json
docs/CI_BASELINE_ZERO.md

# Logs
*.log
logs/
npm-debug.log*

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editor
.vscode/settings.json
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# TypeScript
*.tsbuildinfo

# Test coverage
coverage/
.coverage
backend/.coverage
backend/htmlcov/
frontend/test-results/
frontend/playwright-report/
.mcp.json

# Secrets — private keys, cookies, credentials
*.pem
*.key
ssh_key*
scripts/cookies/
scripts/*_cookies*.txt
scripts/*_cookies*.json
scripts/doubao.txt

# Local debugging artifacts
*.db
*.sqlite
backend/email_previews/
geo_tracker/*.png
gemini_*.png

# UI mockup screenshots — keep outside version control; commit redesign
# captures to the design system instead.
frontend/*.png
